@startuml
title Viaverse Team Execution / Delivery Loop — Activity Diagram
start
:Roadmap item selected;
:Define bounded scope\nuse case + acceptance;
:Design domain model\nAPI/event contracts;
:Break into tasks\nbackend/client/infra/docs;
:Create feature branch\nfrom main/develop;
:Implement vertical slice;
:Unit/integration/contract tests;
:Code review\narchitecture rules;
:Manual QA / UX pass;
:Update docs/UML/ADRs;
:Merge with CI green;
:Deploy to env\nsmoke test;
:Observe metrics/logs\nfeedback;
if (Definition of Done?) then (yes)
  :Phase increment complete;
else (no)
  :Return to backlog\nfix gaps;
  :Re-scope;
endif
stop

note bottom
Every task must connect to a use case, bounded context, contract, test, and documentation update.
Avoid random screen/API coding without domain traceability.
end note
@enduml
